==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Herbivora
<hw>Her*biv"o*ra</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n. pl.</pos> <ety>[NL., fr.
L. <ets>herba</ets> herb + <ets>vorare</ets> to devour.]</ety>
<fld>(Zool.)</fld> <def>An extensive division of Mammalia. It formerly
included the Proboscidea, Hyracoidea, Perissodactyla, and Artiodactyla,
but by later writers it is generally restricted to the two latter groups
(Ungulata). They feed almost exclusively upon vegetation.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Herbivore</ent>⟦br⟧
